      .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) p:not(.skip-text-styles), .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) ul:not(.skip-text-styles), .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) li:not(.skip-text-styles), .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) ol:not(.skip-text-styles), .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) .base-color, .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) .entity-details h3:not(.skip-text-styles), .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) .entity-container:not(.title-overlay) .entity-details .title, html.no-touch .module.secondary-theme:not(.skip-styles) .entity-container.links-out:not(.skip-hover):not(.title-overlay) .entity-details a:hover .title{ color: #000000; }

   /* module-level icon colors */
    .module .module_header.icon .header_icon{
      background-color: #691516;
